1. git clone https://github.com/huawei-noah/streamDM-Cpp.git
2. cd streamDM-Cpp
3. Download latest https://sourceforge.net/projects/log4cpp/  Extract and place log4cpp inside streamDM-Cpp 
4. cd log4cpp
5. ./configure
6. make
7. log4cpp/test/testDailyRollingAppender.cpp -> remove the if condition block with stime.
8. sudo make check
9. sudo make install
10. cd.. to streamDM-Cpp
11. make
12. gedit ~/.bashrc
13. on the bottom of bash, paste this: export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/lib
14. wget "http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/moa-datastream/Datasets/Classification/covtypeNorm.arff.zip"
15. unzip covtypeNorm.arff.zip
